---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
title="How CamCleans Works"
description="Learn how CamCleans connects customers with trusted professional cleaners across the UK."
canonicalPath="/how-camcleans-works"
>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">

    <h1>How CamCleans Works</h1>

    <p class="hero-intro">
      CamCleans connects customers with trusted professional cleaners across the United Kingdom.
      Our platform allows customers to request cleaning services quickly while ensuring every
      cleaner operates to consistent professional standards.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="grid grid-3">

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Submit a Cleaning Request</h2>
        <p>
          Customers request a cleaning service using our enquiry or quote system.
          The request includes the property location, cleaning type and preferred timing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Cleaner Availability</h2>
        <p>
          CamCleans identifies cleaners operating within the relevant area who can
          carry out the requested service and confirm availability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Service Scheduled</h2>
        <p>
          Once availability is confirmed the cleaning appointment is scheduled and
          the customer receives confirmation of the service arrangement.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section section-soft">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Professional Standards</h2>

    <p class="section-intro">
      CamCleans operates with clear expectations for service reliability,
      communication and cleaning quality across all supported services.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Experienced Cleaners</h3>
        <p>
          Cleaners working with CamCleans have relevant experience in domestic
          and specialist cleaning services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Clear Service Expectations</h3>
        <p>
          Cleaning tasks are defined in advance so both customers and cleaners
          understand the service scope before the booking takes place.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Reliable Scheduling</h3>
        <p>
          Cleaning services are arranged for specific dates and times with
          communication provided if scheduling adjustments are required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Consistent Standards</h3>
        <p>
          CamCleans maintains consistent expectations across its cleaning network
          to ensure predictable service outcomes for customers.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section section-cta">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Request a Cleaning Quote</h2>

    <p>
      If you need professional cleaning services, you can request a quote using the
      CamCleans platform.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a class="button" href="/quote">Get a Quote</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>